<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>بِكِلْسٍ وجَيّارٍ <span class="c2">«٢»</span> وجِصٍّ وقَرْمَدِ<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
